The following directory should be added to compiler include paths:

    /home/ruben/Documents/ESPOL/prueba_cpp/boost/boost_1_61_0

The following directory should be added to linker library paths:

    /home/ruben/Documents/ESPOL/prueba_cpp/boost/boost_1_61_0/stage/lib

    cmake -DBOOST_INCLUDEDIR=/home/ruben/Documents/ESPOL/prueba_cpp/boost/boost_1_61_0 -DBOOST_LIBRARYDIR=/home/ruben/Documents/ESPOL/prueba_cpp/boost/boost_1_61_0/stage/lib -DBOOST_VER:STRING=1.6.1 ./
